225
00:28:40.926 --> 00:28:43.405
- Hey.
- Hello.

226
00:28:45.472 --> 00:28:47.272
Nice suit.

227
00:28:47.432 --> 00:28:50.272
Very retro.

228
00:28:50.477 --> 00:28:52.356
Thank you.

229
00:28:55.482 --> 00:28:58.522
Bet that makes
A hell of a cappuccino.

230
00:29:00.281 --> 00:29:02.280
That thing.

231
00:29:05.286 --> 00:29:06.886
I'll see you.

